==English==
===Noun===
'''tetrad'''
# A group of four things.
# '''''Chemistry.''''' A [[tetravalent]] [[atom]] or [[radical]].
# '''''Biology.''''' Two pairs of sister chromatids (a dyad pair) aligned in a certain way and often on the equatorial plane during the meiosis process.

